<!-- src/components/Navbar.vue -->

<template>
  <v-app>
    <v-app-bar app color="primary" dark>
      <v-btn text @click="goToHome">Home</v-btn>
      <v-btn text @click="goToLogin">Login</v-btn>
      <v-btn text @click="goToRegister">Register</v-btn>
      <v-btn text @click="goToManage">Manage</v-btn>
    </v-app-bar>
    <v-main>
      <router-view />
    </v-main>
  </v-app>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  methods: {
    goToHome() {
      this.$router.push("/");
    },
    goToLogin() {
      this.$router.push("/login");
    },
    goToRegister() {
      this.$router.push("/register");
    },
    goToManage() {
      this.$router.push("/manage");
    },
  },
};
</script>
